request.description:
📢 Fetch an accounting entry by his unique origin id or also partners id (The key `entry_origin_partner_id` at the root of the entry payload).

The response is described with the following TypeScript interface:
```ts
interface PartnersEntryMetadata {
  id_entry: number;
  type: "ENTRIES" | "ENTRIES_TEMP";
  json_metadata_partners?: string;
}
```

⚠️ A `society-id` is required with a cabinet/firm access

