request.description:
📢 Company (dossier) Exercices. If an exercise is not closed **closed_at** and **closed_by** are set to `null`.

Exercices labels are `N+1`, `N`, `N-1`, `N-2` etc.

```ts
interface Exercice {
  exercice_id: number;
  start_date: string;
  label: string;
  end_date: string;
  closed: boolean;
  blocked: boolean;
  duration: number;
  result: number;
  ca: number;
  closed_at: null | string;
  closed_by: null | number;
}
```

⚠️ A `society-id` is required with a cabinet/firm access

